      <li>Heitmeyer CL, Marciniak JJ.  2002, "<a href="http://www.nrl.navy.mil/itd/chacs/heitmeyer-software-cost-reduction#in_browser" target="_top">Software Cost Reduction</a>," Encyclopedia of Software Engineering.</li>
